For Arduino project. This project had been tested on ESP8266 Node MCU
Digtail Port 1 = D0
Digtail Port 2 = D1
Digtail Port 3 = D2
Digtail Port 4 = D3
Digtail Port 5 = D4

Analog Port 6   = D5
Analog Port 7   = D6
Analog Port 8   = D7
Analog Port 9   = D8
Analog Port 10  = D5
Analog Port for Servo. For other devices, need to change program 

Note
====
Set Socket IP address : port in Fitbit application setting before start

